lead_paragraph: Title contenders Germany will come face to face with their ultimate tournament nightmare when they take on Italy in their Euro 2016 quarter-final in Bordeaux on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Germany Desperate to Snap Out of Italy Nightmare
